 away.</span></li></ul></div></div></div><p class="sc-daBunf bWmajK pf-112_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ikXwFM hZHGfK pf-114_">To learn more about the sustainability of alpaca wool, see our <a href="https://armsofandes.com/pages/sustainability" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(237, 115, 50);" target="_blank">sustainability page</a>.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-eKYRIR llyViG pf-115_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-hmbstg iriXCP"><div class="sc-hiKfDv dRsyqq pf-116_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-TtZnY gnBPmJ pf-117_"><div class="sc-hiKfDv dRsyqq pf-118_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:8;--c-lg:8"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-TtZnY gnBPmJ pf-119_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-dPaNzc kXWuay pf-120_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ikXwFM hZHGfK pf-122_">4)  LIGHTWEIGHT BACKPACKERS AND TRAVELERS LOVE ALPACA </span></h2><p class="sc-daBunf bWmajK pf-123_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ikXwFM hZHGfK pf-125_">For backpackers and travelers who travel with just a backpack or carry on luggage, space and weight are important considerations when packing. Lightweight items that can be worn on multiple occasions and don’t take up much space, are key. Our <a href="https://armsofandes.com/collections/womens-wool-winter-jackets" target="_blank" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(237, 115, 50);">alpaca sweaters women's collection</a>, like the men’s collection, satisfies those requirements by being:</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-kHWWYL zRuTu pf-126_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-hOPeYd eXirsP pf-127_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ikXwFM hZHGfK pf-129_"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Wrinkle-resistant: